Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.62,0:00:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一點我想先提醒一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.69,0:00:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焰 他不是普通的鶺鴒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.05,0:00:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說下去會惹惱他的我就不多說了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.98,0:00:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道真相的話就抓住他讓他自己坦白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.97,0:01:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26\fad(0,1650)\be1}第六羽\N交合的言語
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.42,0:01:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這兒起就是北區了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.26,0:01:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從出逃者出現後
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.51,0:01:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被認出是鶺鴒 連電車都不讓坐了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.02,0:02:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為盤查變得更嚴了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.65,0:02:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先去找吧 最後一羽No.108
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.52,0:02:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還 還沒有肯定最後一羽就是小草
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.66,0:02:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不是也不能置之不理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.54,0:02:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被奇怪的葦牙抓住了那該多可憐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.70,0:02:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想 不是有過先例嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.28,0:02:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要強吻椎菜的變態
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.33,0:02:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像那種看著就叫人討厭的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.97,0:02:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.68,0:02:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一對一什麼的不用管了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.36,0:02:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陸奧 把那飄啊飄的傢伙幹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.45,0:02:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.16,0:02:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是火焰啊 自然系啊 稀有種啊 我想要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.01,0:02:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陸奧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 您就是南陣營的御子上隼人大人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.23,0:03:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這氣息...是葦牙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.21,0:03:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葦牙！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.61,0:03:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 那飄啊飄的是你的鶺鴒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.66,0:03:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且算是我們的手下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.60,0:03:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本人是東陣營的冰峨泉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.30,0:03:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東陣營的冰峨？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.90,0:03:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的秘書 柿崎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.91,0:03:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後大家就算認識了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.05,0:03:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶺鴒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.05,0:03:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不必擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.84,0:03:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在捕獲No.06前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.47,0:03:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你們能夠老實待著 是什麼也不會做的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.83,0:03:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火大！這大人竟繞著圈子洗刷我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.26,0:03:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陸奧 幹掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.01,0:03:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說得真輕巧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.78,0:03:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能再帶兩三羽來的話 就另當別論了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.58,0:03:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來現在最後的一羽已經不是重點了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.02,0:04:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我親你也可以哦 祝詞祝詞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝詞祝詞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.16,0:04:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 管他5羽還是10羽都跟我沒關係呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.54,0:04:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋津 撤了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.12,0:04:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？要跑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已經不行了 放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.35,0:04:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 白跑一趟？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.51,0:04:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你問過我為什麼會有主人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.69,0:04:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.25,0:04:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有絲毫猶豫的好眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.42,0:04:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了葦牙連死都不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.42,0:04:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.27,0:04:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是因為成為了葦牙 就是主人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.82,0:04:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是因為自己認可其為主人 我如此認為
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.74,0:05:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是面對這個壞掉了的我 他也說想要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.85,0:05:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算身體上刻不了他的印記
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.19,0:05:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也依舊是我的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.07,0:05:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是能夠羽化的吧 真叫人羨慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.57,0:05:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.84,0:05:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才有一聲巨響呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.24,0:05:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人捷足先登了？快跑椎菜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.76,0:05:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤佳里 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.42,0:05:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 給我小心點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.28,0:05:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然跑出來的不是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.76,0:05:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什...可不是你...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.90,0:05:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.49,0:05:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膝蓋...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.53,0:05:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 少女的玉足被磨破了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.96,0:05:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.91,0:05:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這種小傷弄點唾沫就搞掂了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.35,0:06:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了 椎菜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好個瘋丫頭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.77,0:06:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踢得挺狠的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.97,0:06:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要老實聽話 我是不會殺你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.68,0:06:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶺鴒的守護者？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.79,0:06:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少在與葦牙邂逅前 能有個人保護她們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.72,0:06:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會接受嗎 焰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.96,0:06:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些孩子...我所保護的孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.36,0:06:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果與葦牙邂逅了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.15,0:06:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...就滿足了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.67,0:06:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...沒能親手除掉御中...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.75,0:07:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焰！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.01,0:07:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就交給我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.51,0:07:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈿女 你...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.99,0:07:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽化前 羽化前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.81,0:07:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在燃燒哦 柿崎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.82,0:07:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.01,0:07:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一個體的輸出很不穩定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.66,0:07:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道配不配當冰峨大人的鶺鴒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.95,0:07:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰峨？東陣營的葦牙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.76,0:07:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.29,0:07:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣的一個遊戲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.20,0:07:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是遺憾了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.37,0:07:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們白跑一趟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.71,0:07:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御中！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.31,0:07:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其成為你設定的遊戲的獎品
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.74,0:07:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我寧可在這裡溶掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.54,0:07:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.06焰的死法 好好看著吧 御中！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.74,0:08:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美哉 高美小姐 我...已經...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.47,0:08:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣也配當吾之敵手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿松很擔心篝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.19,0:08:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我...只是擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.69,0:08:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.72,0:08:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爾在做些什麼 焰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.98,0:08:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾應該已經說過 不允許爾止步不前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.62,0:08:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.25,0:08:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西陣營的真田嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:08:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.30,0:09:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北陣營 嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.56,0:09:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們...為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.91,0:09:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.31,0:09:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝...沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.93,0:09:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐橋？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.83,0:09:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說過不需要什麼同情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.39,0:09:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是同情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 這不是同情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.69,0:09:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結我們 是來找你要房租的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.68,0:09:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小 小結...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.59,0:09:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.11,0:09:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爾竟然蒙蔽吾至今
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.09,0:09:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去以後做好覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.65,0:09:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝 我們來接你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.68,0:09:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是讓你隨隨便便殺了社長我可就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.59,0:09:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舊戀的回憶依舊美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.93,0:09:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 並非有所留戀哦 絕非
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.70,0:09:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留戀？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.83,0:09:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是敵人嗎 怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.16,0:09:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說其就快壞掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.06,0:09:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但羽化前的鶺鴒在眼前被帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.41,0:09:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是叫人很火大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.35,0:09:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 搞掉她們？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.19,0:10:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你當然也要一起戰鬥哦 No.10
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙 是戴比禮頭巾的鶺鴒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.36,0:10:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是冤家路窄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.22,0:10:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 那孩子由我來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.52,0:10:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟有規定 我姑且還是報下名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.54,0:10:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.101 織刃 葦牙是冰峨泉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.24,0:10:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷襲嗎 自以為是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.34,0:10:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點毅力就想向吾宣戰膽子不小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.09 月海
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.31,0:10:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找上門來的戰鬥 將加倍奉還
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.48,0:10:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.88 結 拳系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.84,0:10:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.86 葛城 腿系...吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.31,0:10:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.87,0:10:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一點都不吃驚呢 看到我在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.18,0:10:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.54,0:11:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道你有你的理由 也預想過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.45,0:11:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,襲擊No.95 以及向我挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.46,0:11:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一瞬間想要觸碰我的鶺鴒紋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.10,0:11:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有默不作聲離開出雲莊的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.63,0:11:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為美哉跟我 還有松都不會注意到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.06,0:11:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是敵不過姐姐你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.06,0:11:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.23,0:11:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切都是為了葦牙 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.71,0:11:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能讓鶺鴒戰鬥的理由 僅此而已了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀～是戀愛呢 是戀愛吧 啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.76,0:11:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 之前的嚴肅氛圍全浪費了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.89,0:11:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 作為鶺鴒是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.69,0:11:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我就跟你戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.70,0:11:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.29,0:11:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 為什麼會如此居高臨下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.80,0:11:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 姐姐的這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.58,0:11:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在讓我得到了莫大的救贖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.80,0:12:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是住在北之般若那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.94,0:12:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況複雜的葦牙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.45,0:12:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乍看只是個不起眼的青年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潛過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.30,0:12:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.56,0:12:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝 我們之所以在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.70,0:12:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是因為同情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.77,0:12:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.24,0:12:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你...能成為我的鶺鴒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.66,0:12:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.56,0:12:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟那些被短信引過來的傢伙一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.49,0:12:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有御中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.26,0:12:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你來說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.06,0:12:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我也只是一場遊戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.93,0:12:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要的是我的力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.19,0:12:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼想要一大堆鶺鴒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.73,0:12:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不巧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.14,0:12:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經壞掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.06,0:13:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很醜陋吧 這副身體
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連是男是女都分不清
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.31,0:13:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能力也不穩定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.64,0:13:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就連為了自己活著都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.52,0:13:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.66,0:13:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要在這裡燃燒殆盡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.76,0:13:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從最開始就不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.04,0:13:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我存在的意義什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.64,0:13:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好燙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.06,0:13:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼 放開
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.28,0:13:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會燒死的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.62,0:13:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不放
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.74,0:13:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能沒意義呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.12,0:13:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐橋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.78,0:13:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝是出雲莊重要的夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.65,0:13:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.94,0:13:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟小結從天上掉下來受傷那時
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.56,0:13:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幫我治療
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.57,0:13:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被趕出了公寓 迷惘不知所措的我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.34,0:13:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我住進了出雲莊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.96,0:13:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時我真的很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.41,0:14:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那點小事...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.69,0:14:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了 快放開
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.41,0:14:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽老媽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小結 小草都得到篝的幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.95,0:14:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月海也說你是她不想失去的好敵手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.90,0:14:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都想救你 才來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.72,0:14:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們的思念 我的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.11,0:14:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是什麼遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.08,0:14:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.02,0:14:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.18,0:14:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開我 我已經控制不了能力了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.94,0:14:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我絕對不會讓你死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.96,0:14:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞定 終於成功了 皆人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.28,0:14:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 他幹什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.47,0:15:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 皆人他...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.81,0:15:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦啊啦 這...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.61,0:15:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.91,0:15:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.43,0:15:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火焰受控了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.50,0:15:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.94,0:15:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炙烤身體的熱量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.43,0:15:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全身的刺痛都消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.10,0:15:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經乖離的力量和身體
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.57,0:15:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種跟靈魂同化的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.37,0:15:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.68,0:15:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是隻特殊的鶺鴒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.72,0:15:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定能羽化你的葦牙並不存在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.15,0:15:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 這僅限於現在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.09,0:15:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葦牙的力量 就是「緣」的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.00,0:15:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思念他人的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.91,0:15:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羈絆越深越強 葦牙的力量就會增強
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.87,0:16:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天會有人來到你身邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.91,0:16:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伴著緣 成為「原初存在」的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.22,0:16:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你的葦牙...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.38,0:16:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.26,0:16:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎停了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.23,0:16:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.22,0:16:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐橋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.28,0:16:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.61,0:16:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你傻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.40,0:16:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然跳進火海
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老媽說 讓你羽化 能力說不定就會穩定下來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.67,0:16:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我...那個 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.33,0:16:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你是為親了我道歉？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.55,0:16:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 很對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.21,0:16:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你這男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.40,0:16:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 感覺無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.05,0:16:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在覺得鑽牛角尖就像個笨蛋一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.99,0:16:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會負責任吧 佐橋皆人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.40,0:16:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,責 責任？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.34,0:16:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,責任是指...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.69,0:16:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「常伴你身邊」？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.71,0:17:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是鶺鴒的台詞啊 蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.60,0:17:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 美哉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來有趣的事情要發生了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾的確說了要娶他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.85,0:17:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過夫君在面前跟其他人接 接 接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.74,0:17:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶺鴒是很有趣的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.64,0:17:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心之所在·靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.25,0:17:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會按照其真實形態表現出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.64,0:17:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憤怒 憎恨 喜悅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.52,0:17:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當中還有戀愛感情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.04,0:17:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情的振幅越大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對能力的影響也顯著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.31,0:17:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我察覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.49,0:17:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很無趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常的修煉不過是提高她們的能力水平
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.52,0:17:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們自己應該也有相當的成長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.10,0:17:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我胸中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.20,0:17:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相當無趣！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.40,0:17:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會出現什麼呢 真期待
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.52,0:18:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.65,0:18:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八歧大蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.69,0:18:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都在 黑色的野獸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.96,0:18:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.80,0:18:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小結體內的 黑熊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.22,0:18:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊拳！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.10,0:18:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.65,0:18:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 蛇啊 我討厭蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.46,0:18:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畜生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.72,0:18:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少扯淡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.55,0:18:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 你怎麼被抓住了 柿崎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.44,0:18:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在丟臉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.03,0:19:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.06已經羽化了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.87,0:19:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連葛城都被幹翻了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.37,0:19:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果冰峨大人在的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.83,0:19:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能用祝詞對付這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.10,0:19:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.80,0:19:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織刃 正是冰峨大人 撤退命令
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.85,0:19:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真強啊 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.67,0:19:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的很強
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.17,0:19:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然之前就聽說到No.05都不是一般的強
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.71,0:19:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是經驗豐富罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各種各樣的 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.78,0:19:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我也決不能輸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.21,0:19:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真棒 認真的眼神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.02,0:19:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是戀愛中人的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.54,0:19:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.10 撤退命令
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.58,0:19:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然火大 但要撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.86,0:19:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你撿回一條命了呢 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.92,0:19:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我要說的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.51,0:19:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.49,0:20:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 結束了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.85,0:20:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想看看都有些什麼人聚在一塊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.69,0:20:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 回去吧 我的小可愛們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.11,0:20:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住 竟然逃跑 卑鄙之極
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.17,0:20:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉～我這邊也讓人跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.74,0:20:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 下次碰面一定收拾她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.93,0:20:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小結呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.74,0:20:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶺鴒機能停止的場合
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.82,0:20:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在MBI過來回收之前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在身旁守護也是戰鬥中的禮儀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.77,0:20:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我們回去吧 皆人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.52,0:20:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.33,0:20:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.48,0:20:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回出雲莊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.39,0:21:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話 頭腦還很混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.23,0:21:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 心情已經平和了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.55,0:21:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常伴 你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.06,0:21:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼～告一段落
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.94,0:21:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是告一段落 而是開端
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.26,0:21:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焰以外的所有鶺鴒都完成了羽化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.15,0:21:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就是真正的開始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.08,0:21:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以帝都為舞台的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.28,0:21:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掀起腥風血雨的真正戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,/ED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.81,0:23:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿松 下一集會講什麼故事？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.19,0:23:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的台詞量不是一般的多
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.19,0:23:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不 總之我要說個不停
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.38,0:23:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要開個阿松大遊行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.44,0:23:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集是 「阿松不斷講」這一則故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.62,0:23:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個標題會不會...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.90,0:23:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第七羽 久遠故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.94,0:23:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集也常伴你身邊
